# HyperAgent CLI
#
# This repo uses a SINGLE root dotenv source of truth.
#
# 1) Copy the root template:
#    cp ../../.env.example ../../.env
#
# 2) Edit ../../.env and set at minimum:
#    - GEMINI_API_KEY (or OPENAI_API_KEY / ANTHROPIC_API_KEY)
#    - THIRDWEB_CLIENT_ID (if using x402 features)
#
# Note:
# - The CLI loads env from the repo root via @hyperagent/env.
